VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'can\'t get in front of a camera, and then you could use that audio inside the &gt;&gt; [music] &gt;&gt; speech section. So, just to set the stage, I\'m going to use some audio from a very old video when I used to wear glasses here. So, don\'t laugh. This is when Clean 2.0 launched, and we thought'

[15:15] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'it was the coolest thing in the entire world because it was at the time. So, this is real video footage back then. Clean 2.0 is here and it\'s taking over social media, but the big question is,'

[15:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'how does it stack up against other AI video tools? &gt;&gt; I think the big question is, why were you wearing a Santa Claus jacket inside a video there, sir? Okay, so I\'m going to take that audio from that video. So,'

[15:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'this is real audio from that video and bring it inside of 11 Labs to see how well the lip sync operates. [music] So, I\'ll grab that OG audio, drop it into the speech section here, and you do'

[15:52] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'have the ability to type in a prompt to push the video in a specific direction. This is where you can add in more information about how you want your character to be expressive and just'

